I even have to prepare the decorations.

76
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,070
Am I proposing or him?

77
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,600
Seriously, everything Wei does
is one step ahead of me.

78
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,680
Even proposing.

79
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,680
Can't he let me win once?

80
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,680
What now?

81
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:33,190
You don't want to give Wei ideas

82
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,360
