You don't want to?

92
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:12,830
No.

93
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,360
I just think

94
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,720
that my girlfriend is too great.

95
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,870
