99
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,560
Mr. Wei Ziqi,

100
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,310
if one day,

101
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:55,040
your relationship status
becomes widowed,

102
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,430
would you regret it?

103
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,600
If it were you,

104
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,600
would you?

105
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,560
Of course, I won't.

106
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,120
I will follow my wife.

107
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,270
My answer is the same as yours.

108
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,510
Just one final step.

109
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,040
Ms. Yuan Xia,

110
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,680
will you marry me?

111
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:45,160
I...

112
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:50,830
I think the formality
is not proper enough.

113
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,160
Ms. Yuan Xia,

114
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,750
will you marry me?

115
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,240
I will.

116
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:22,540
♪To reunite with you♪

117
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:29,580
♪If time could testify♪

118
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:34,540
♪I've searched for it
over and over again♪

119
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:39,180
♪For the same look in your eyes
as before♪

120
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:41,620
♪This voiceless yearning♪

121
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:43,580
♪Transcends time and space♪

122
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,420
♪Love redeems each other♪

123
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,840
Then let's now proceed

124
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:50,270
with the final step in the process.

125
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:55,900
♪Two could become one♪

126
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:59,060
♪I believe love can turn♪

127
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:02,500
♪The gears of fate♪

128
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:04,740
♪I've confirmed♪

129
00:09:04,940 --> 00:09:06,500
♪All the paths♪

130
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,380
♪And all paths lead♪

131
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:11,500
♪to the door of your heart♪

132
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:14,060
♪I'll continue to love you
despite the future♪

133
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:17,420
♪Is full of different possibilities♪

134
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:20,980
♪Hold you tighter by a fraction♪

135
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:23,620
♪Just like this until♪

136
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:25,900
♪The end of time♪

137
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:29,980
♪Let love take root♪

138
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:37,870
Finally done.

139
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:40,030
This is more tiring than a day of work.

140
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,630
It's pretty.

141
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:44,840
Of course.

142
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:48,500
(Wei Ziqi)

143
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,320
Hey, Wei.

144
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:55,150
We're almost done here.

145
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,030
Have you set off?

146
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,510
Can we be on standby?

147
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,030
We aren't going there anymore.

148
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:05,630
Okay.

149
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:08,480
What did you just say?

150
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,670
You're not coming?

151
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:10,960
We were so busy

152
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,870
preparing everything.

153
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,430
Now you're saying
you aren't coming over?

154
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,670
Aren't you going to propose?

155
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:16,440
No. What do you mean?

156
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,080
What do you mean by not proposing?

157
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:20,270
Because I've already been proposed to.

158
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,510
And I've already agreed,

159
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,840
so the proposal ceremony is completed.

160
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,000
It's hard to make a reservation
at that restaurant.

161
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,900
I booked the whole venue.

162
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:31,240
I'll leave the dinner to you two.

163
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,120
Don't waste it.

164
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,390
Let's make a bet.

165
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:37,630
Do you think Xing Nan will confess?

166
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:41,320
We've created opportunities
to this point.

167
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,910
If he doesn't confess

168
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,250
he deserves to be single
for the rest of his life.

169
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,030
Happy Wedding.

170
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,750
Happy Wedding.

171
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,600
Such a gentleman.

172
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,120
Dr. Xing,

173
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,000
could it be that

174
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,910
you have an ulterior motive?

175
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,750
What ulterior motives can I have?

176
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,320
I just noticed how clumsy you are.

177
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,840
What crime did this cattle commit?

178
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,320
It was killed while alive.

179
00:11:45,450 --> 00:11:47,475
Even in death, it has to
be cut into pieces by you.

180
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,240
I thought

181
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,480
you wanted to take this opportunity

182
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,790
to tell me something.

183
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,720
Well.

184
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,030
What do you want me to express?

185
00:12:10,850 --> 00:12:14,840
Should you really
be asking this to a girl?

186
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,000
Ni Ning.

187
00:12:31,725 --> 00:12:33,200
Actually, I have never been in love.

188
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,670
All my relationship skills
and ways to seduce people

189
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,670
including...

190
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,200
Including the setup for today's proposal

191
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,510
are all that I read on Zhihu and Baidu.

192
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,080
I didn't know

193
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,630
how it felt to like somebody

194
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,000
until I met someone.

195
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,120
Thanks.

196
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,875
Whenever I see her, I blush
and my heart beats faster.

197
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,630
I would overthink her words.

198
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,360
And in my mind,

199
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,630
her figure frequently appears.

200
00:13:07,975 --> 00:13:09,320
Don't be afraid. Just look at her.

201
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,270
You're a veteran, Dr. Xing.

202
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,840
Can I interpret this

203
00:13:16,030 --> 00:13:17,120
as you teasing me?

204
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,440
When you ride a motorcycle,

205
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,360
are you wearing a helmet?

206
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:28,630
When you are fighting,

207
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:30,300
would you get injured
from trying too hard?

208
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:31,240
I...

209
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,630
I searched on Zhihu and Baidu.

210
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:36,600
They say I like her.

211
00:13:39,270 --> 00:13:40,120
That's right, Ni Ning.

212
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,670
I've fallen in love with you.

213
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:46,790
Didn't you ask me

214
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:48,360
if I wanted to express something to you?

215
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,030
I...

216
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,030
I'll admit it.

217
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,510
Actually, for myself,

218
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:55,070
there is a hurdle in my heart
that I have not been able to overcome.

219
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:55,910
In love,

220
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:58,270
I always feel like a loser.

221
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,750
So I always retreat at critical moments.

222
00:14:00,975 --> 00:14:02,120
I obviously like you very much.

223
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,270
I really want to be with you.

224
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,910
But I don't dare to tell you.

225
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,030
I could only use some clumsy techniques

226
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:08,080
to come near you.

227
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,270
Recently,

228
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:14,670
the things that happened between Wei
and Yuan Xia have reminded me

229
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:18,270
that meeting someone
you like is not easy.

230
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:21,375
Moreover, we can stay together
for a lifetime.

231
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,240
So,

232
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,270
I don't want my cowardice

233
00:14:27,270 --> 00:14:28,440
to be the cause of missing you.

234
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,300
I would regret it for the rest
of my life.

235
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,630
Are you sure?

236
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:41,720
People like me

237
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:43,480
like excitement

238
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,910
and challenges.

239
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,960
I also like to keep pushing forward.

240
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,510
It is impossible for me

241
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:53,000
to retreat to the background willingly
for somebody's sake.

242
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:55,600
I will probably always be like this.

243
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:57,080
I will keep pushing forward.

244
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:59,000
And my life

245
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:01,840
will always be full of danger.

246
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,550
Feel free to charge forward.

247
00:15:04,975 --> 00:15:06,320
Don't forget what I do for a living.

248
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,960
If you get hurt, I will bandage it.

249
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,600
If you die, I will perform CPR on you.

250
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:10,960
Moreover,

251
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,200
didn't you say

252
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:14,790
that you always wanted to sleep with me?

253
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:18,840
Sure, I will let you sleep with me.

254
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,720
Are you crazy?

255
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,030
I'm not finished yet.

256
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,150
I don't accept a fling.

257
00:15:24,075 --> 00:15:25,850
I only accept official relationships.

258
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,840
Sure, you can sleep with me.

259
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,775
But you must be responsible for it.

260
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,440
Ni Ning.

261
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,320
I like you.

262
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:40,270
Would you like to be with me?

263
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,200
To be honest,

264
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:52,080
I never thought

265
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,630
I would be responsible for other lives.

266
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:57,320
Before this, when I was bored,

267
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,630
I thought about getting a pet.

268
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:00,720
But I'm afraid it will become
a burden to me.

269
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,120
I didn't dare to get one.

270
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:03,790
This was also the reason

271
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:06,630
I wanted to push you away before this.

272
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:09,390
Later,

273
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:11,550
it was the first time

274
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,480
somebody stopped my car

275
00:16:16,725 --> 00:16:18,350
while I was on my way to my mission.

276
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,390
It was the first time

277
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:22,480
somebody blocked all the sunlight for me

278
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,750
after my mission ended

279
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,630
just so I could have a good sleep.

280
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:31,440
Maybe from then onwards,

281
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:33,910
I feel like the burden
has turned into worry.

282
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:38,240
I started to think that
